# 🚀 Kicau Store Backend

Backend REST API menggunakan NestJS, TypeORM, dan MySQL.

## Teknologi

- NestJS
- TypeORM
- MySQL
- REST API

## Instalasi

```bash
npm install
```

## Menjalankan

```bash
npm run start:dev
```

Server berjalan di

```
http://localhost:3000
```

---

## Database

Database

```
kicau_store
```

---

## Endpoint

### GET Semua Produk

```
GET /products
```

### GET Produk Berdasarkan ID

```
GET /products/:id
```

### POST Produk

```
POST /products
```

### PATCH Produk

```
PATCH /products/:id
```

### DELETE Produk

```
DELETE /products/:id
```

---

## Entity Product

- id
- name
- description
- category
- image
- price
- stock

